The traditional strengths of
YouTube, which is creation and

00:01:55.690 --> 00:01:57.630
platform for content creation.

00:01:57.630 --> 00:02:00.440
We'll talk about curation, which
is something new that we

00:02:00.440 --> 00:02:03.160
have been working on, and we
have a wonderful developer

00:02:03.160 --> 00:02:06.300
ecosystem around it as well, a
lot of innovative companies

00:02:06.300 --> 00:02:08.240
trying to surface content.

00:02:08.240 --> 00:02:10.610
And then we'll talk about
beautiful consumption

00:02:10.610 --> 00:02:11.230
experience.

00:02:11.230 --> 00:02:13.650
And again, for all three of
them, we will talk about what

00:02:13.650 --> 00:02:16.990
we do to enable it from API
